Introduction

This document describes the

Examples and Tutorials

A quick start guide covering how to use the adapter in your GWT application is available on the front page of the StreamHub GWT Adapter Project.

There are GWT examples available to view on the StreamHub Examples page. The source code for these examples can be browsed online (Browse Source Code) or checked out (Check Out Source Code).

The latest tutorials, news and getting started guides for StreamHub in general are available on the StreamHub Comet Blog. More examples are available in the SDK available to download from the StreamHub website.

Support

Commercial customers should contact the StreamHub Support Team at support@stream-hub.com quoting their unique support key.

Community edition users can seek help in the StreamHub Comet Server Community on Google Groups.
